  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>There's three cosy dining rooms at the hotel where a varied buffet breakfast and five-course dinners are served. Expect international and local dishes on the menu using high-quality ingredients. Once a week there’s a Tyrolean evening with lots of local food to try.</p>
<p>Packed lunches are available on request. These are great to take with you when you're walking in the mountains.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
