  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Val Gardena Active Programme partner accommodation</strong></p>
<p>Hotel Rodella is an affiliate of the <a rel="noopener" href="https://www.valgardena-active.com/en/summer" target="_blank">Val Gardena Active</a> programme so you can join free or discounted activities every day of the week (activities are bookable and payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Hotel facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Panoramic heated pool that leads from inside the spa to the outdoor pool on the garden terrace</li>
<li>Spa with Finnish sauna, steam bath, sensory showers and relaxation area with views of the Sella mountains</li>
<li>Panoramic sun terrace with loungers</li>
<li>Pool and spa towels provided free of charge</li>
<li>Massages and beauty treatments are payable locally</li>
<li>Table football</li>
<li>Lounge bar</li>
<li>Free shuttle service to the centre of Selva (on request)</li>
<li>The hotel has a 4* Natura classification - using 100% green energy</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Free parking</li>
<li>Garage (payable locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
