  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Comfort Rooms</strong> are about 25<span>m² and sleep two people.</span></p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> are about 28<span>m² and </span>sleep up to four people (extra bed is a single or a double sofa bed). They have a comfy seating area.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are about 32<span>m² and sleep up to four people (extra bed is a single or a double sofa bed). They have a comfy seating area.</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Comfort Rooms for sole use</strong> are available on request, please call to book.</span></p>
<p>Please request twin or double beds at the time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony with mountain views</li>
<li>Shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Spa bag with bathrobes, slippers and towel</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request for approx. €10 per day, payable locally. </p>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €2.50 per person per night is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
